==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Koolokamba
<hw>Koo`lo*kam"ba</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A west African anthropoid ape (<spn>Troglodytes koolokamba</spn>,
or <spn>Troglodytes Aubryi</spn>), allied to the chimpanzee and gorilla,
and, in some respects, intermediate between them.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Koolslaa</ent>⟦br⟧
